title: Conquest Reimagined Alpha Gameplay LIVE! | Lord of the Rings Gaming
description:
We're playing the brand new Alpha demo for the fan-made "Conquest Reimagined" - a remake of the classic Lord of the Rings: Conquest game from 2009!

To find out more about Conquest Reimagined, visit: https://conquestreimagined.org/

What is Conquest: Reimagined?
Conquest: Reimagined is a non-commercial fan made game remastering and adding new features to the game “Lord of the Rings: Conquest" developed by Pandemic Studio and Published by EA in January of 2009. This game is still under development.
